Interface ObjectListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ListenerAttribute, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ConsoleListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    History, ModuleExit, ModuleJarLoader, ModuleListener

    public interface ObjectListener
extends java.io.Serializable, ListenerAttribute
    Interface for classes that wish to get notified when the listener is sent an object.

    v5.0
    See Also:
